      <div class="panel info"><span class="panel-icon">💡</span><div class="panel-content"><strong>Approach — Sort + Linear Scan</strong>Sort intervals by start. Iterate: if the current interval overlaps with the last merged one (start ≤ prev end), extend the end. Otherwise push the current as a new interval.</div></div>
