    <div class="problem-card-body">
      <div class="technique-row"><span class="technique-label">🎯 Technique</span><span class="tag tag-blue">Matrix Manipulation</span><span class="tag tag-purple">Transpose + Reverse</span></div>
      <div class="panel info"><span class="panel-icon">💡</span><div class="panel-content"><strong>Approach — Transpose then Reverse Rows</strong>A 90° clockwise rotation equals: (1) Transpose the matrix (swap <code>[i][j]</code> ↔ <code>[j][i]</code>), then (2) reverse each row. Both steps are done in-place with O(1) extra space.</div></div>
      <table class="complexity-table"><thead><tr><th>Metric</th><th>Complexity</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Time</td><td class="complexity-time">O(n²)</td><td>Visit every cell</td></tr><tr><td>Space</td><td class="complexity-space">O(1)</td><td>In-place</td></tr></tbody></table>
      <div class="code-block"><div class="code-header"><span class="code-lang">Java</span><span class="code-title">Rotate Image — Transpose + Reverse</span></div><pre><span class="kw">class</span> <span class="tp">Solution</span> {
    <span class="kw">public void</span> <span class="fn">rotate</span>(<span class="kw">int</span>[][] matrix) {
        <span class="kw">int</span> n = matrix.length;
        <span class="cm">// Step 1: Transpose</span>
        <span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nm">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++)
            <span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> j = i+<span class="nm">1</span>; j &lt; n; j++) {
                <span class="kw">int</span> tmp = matrix[i][j]; matrix[i][j] = matrix[j][i]; matrix[j][i] = tmp;
            }
        <span class="cm">// Step 2: Reverse each row</span>
        <span class="kw">for</span> (<span class="kw">int</span> i = <span class="nm">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) {
            <span class="kw">int</span> l = <span class="nm">0</span>, r = n-<span class="nm">1</span>;
            <span class="kw">while</span> (l &lt; r) { <span class="kw">int</span> tmp=matrix[i][l]; matrix[i][l++]=matrix[i][r]; matrix[i][r--]=tmp; }
        }
    }
}</pre></div>
    </div>
