      <div class="panel info"><span class="panel-icon">💡</span><div class="panel-content"><strong>Approach — Two Pointers (Inward Scan)</strong>Use left and right pointers moving inward. Skip non-alphanumeric characters. Compare remaining characters case-insensitively. If any mismatch is found, return false.</div></div>
      <table class="complexity-table"><thead><tr><th>Metric</th><th>Complexity</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Time</td><td class="complexity-time">O(n)</td><td>Each char visited once</td></tr><tr><td>Space</td><td class="complexity-space">O(1)</td><td>No extra allocation</td></tr></tbody></table>
      <div class="code-block"><div class="code-header"><span class="code-lang">Java</span><span class="code-title">Valid Palindrome</span></div><pre><span class="kw">class</span> <span class="tp">Solution</span> {
