  <div class="problem-card"><div class="problem-card-header"><span class="problem-number">#78</span><h3 class="problem-heading" style="margin:0">Subsets</h3><span class="tag tag-orange">Medium</span></div><div class="problem-card-body"><div class="technique-row"><span class="technique-label">🎯 Technique</span><span class="tag tag-blue">Backtracking</span><span class="tag tag-purple">Include/Skip Recursion</span></div><div class="panel info"><span class="panel-icon">💡</span><div class="panel-content"><strong>Approach — Backtracking (Add at Every Node)</strong>Add the current combination to results at every recursive call (not just leaf). Then for each remaining element, choose it, recurse, and unchoose. Generates all 2ⁿ subsets.</div></div><table class="complexity-table"><thead><tr><th>Metric</th><th>Complexity</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Time</td><td class="complexity-time">O(n × 2ⁿ)</td><td>2ⁿ subsets, each up to n long</td></tr><tr><td>Space</td><td class="complexity-space">O(n)</td><td>Recursion depth</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="code-block"><div class="code-header"><span class="code-lang">Java</span></div><pre><span class="kw">class</span> <span class="tp">Solution</span> {
